text: Alexander Gahon Gesmundo (born November 6, 1956) is a Filipino politician and lawyer. In 2021, he became the Chief Justice of the Philippines. He was an Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the Philippines from 2017 to 2021. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Chief justices of the Supreme Court of the Philippines Category:People from Laguna (province)
title: Alexander Gesmundo
